<div class="anchor-example">
  <h2 style="margin-bottom: 24px">Link</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'Link voorbeeld', url:"#"} %}
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'Externe link', url:"#", modifier:"extern") %}
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'Download link', url:"#", modifier:"download") %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h3 class="toolkit-example-label">Voorbeeld in lopende tekst:</h3>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing
        elit. Aenean commodo ligula eget dolor. Nullam dictum
        felis eu pede {% render '@anchor', {label: 'mollis pretium', url: '#', modifier: 'extern') %}. Integer tincidunt. Cras dapibus.
        Vivamus {% render '@anchor', {label: 'elementum', url: '#', modifier: 'extern') %} semper nisi. Aenean vulputate
        eleifend tellus. Aenean leo ligula, porttitor eu,
        consequat vitae, eleifend ac, enim. Aliquam lorem ante,
        dapibus in, viverra quis, feugiat a, tellus. Phasellus
        viverra nulla ut metus varius laoreet. Quisque rutrum.
        Aenean imperdiet. Etiam ultricies nisi vel augue.
        Curabitur ullamcorper <a class="download" href="#">ultricies nisi</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 style="margin-bottom: 24px">Visueel als buttons</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'Anchor', modifier:'dso-primary', url:'#'} %}
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'Anchor', modifier:'dso-secondary', url:'#'} %}
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2">
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'.btn-align', modifier:'dso-tertiary btn-align', url:'#'} %}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'Link button', modifier:'dso-tertiary', url:'#'} %}
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'Link button', modifier:'dso-tertiary', icon:'info', iconOnly:true, url:'#'} %}
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'Link button', modifier:'dso-tertiary', icon:'angle-left', url:'#'} %}
      {% render '@anchor', {label:'Link button', modifier:'dso-tertiary', iconAfter:'angle-right', url:'#'} %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
